{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"5b0a18e6b8","title":"对金门蒋军向我炮击的处置意见的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"113ecd2343","index":0,"year":1960,"month":8,"day":7,"articleId":"5b0a18e6b8"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji43","name":"毛泽东全集第43卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/43-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji43":{"comments":[{"id":"46d6753dd9","publicationId":"maoquanji43","articleId":"5b0a18e6b8","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这是毛泽东对中共中央军委秘书长、中国人民解放军总参谋长、国务院副总理罗瑞卿1960年8月5日报告的批语。"},{"id":"0d8ce0b9c6","publicationId":"maoquanji43","articleId":"5b0a18e6b8","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"罗瑞卿的报告汇报了金门国民党军在一段时间内向我炮击的情况，并提出四点意见：（一）立即加强侦察措施，进一步查明故人这一炮击的企图。（二）对敌人的零星炮击，我可暂不置理。（三）如故继续打炮，对我造成危害，我即考虑采取压制或惩罚性的炮击，但这种炮击，应报中央军委决定。（四）不管敌人的炮击企图如何，我厦门前线部队均应适当加以戒备。"}],"contents":[{"id":"4b53f432ef","type":"title","text":"对金门将军向我炮击的处置意见的批语则","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji43","articleId":"5b0a18e6b8"},{"id":"46d6753dd9","type":"subtitle","text":"照办。P","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji43","articleId":"5b0a18e6b8"},{"id":"0d8ce0b9c6","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji43","articleId":"5b0a18e6b8"},{"id":"3e17a315da","type":"paragraph","text":"八月七日","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji43","articleId":"5b0a18e6b8"}],"page":{"id":"0a54f980f4","publicationId":"maoquanji43","articleId":"5b0a18e6b8","start":463,"end":463}}}},"__N_SSG":true}